<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.4.1.min.js" integrity="sha256-CSXorXvZcTkaix6Yvo6HppcZGetbYMGWSFlBw8HfCJo=" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/popper.js/1.14.7/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.3.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/standard_style.css' />
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/text_animation.css' />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="16x16" href="/images/assets/Logo.png">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/images/assets/Logo.png">

  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="screensized_container" style="justify-content: center; display: flex;">
      <div style="justify-content: center; display: flex; flex-direction: column; text-align: center; width: 500px;">
        <div class="title_container" style="margin-bottom: 0px; display: flex; justify-content: center;">
          <img class="asset" style="width: 35vw;" src="/images/assets/tornpage.png">
          <div class="title" style="top:60%; font-size: 2vw;">Not&nbsp;A&nbsp;Fairy&nbsp;Tale</div>
        </div>
        <div style="font: 20px Catamaran; color: white;">
          A game about the perspective of a child<br>stuck in the institute
        </div>
        <div style="font: 15px Catamaran; color: white; width: 400px; margin: 10px 50px;">
          based on the perspective of an orpan child, 'Not A Fairy Tale' seeks to put a spotlight on the experiences that children have when placed under institutional care. It aims to ignite empathy amongst the general masses and to ensure the stories of those in the system aren't forgotten.
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style=" justify-content: center; display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
        <img class="asset" style="height: 500px; width: 350px; transform: rotate(3deg);" src="/images/art/NotAFairyTalePoster.jpg">
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="title_container" style="text-align: center;">
      <img src="/images/assets/brushstroke1.png" height:100%; top:0;>
      <div class="title">Concept Art</div>
    </div>

    <div class="container" style="font: 16px Catamaran; justify-content: center; display: flex; color: white; font-size: 16px; width: 700px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
      Tasked as the head visual designer of the project, I had the responsibility of creating a rich, compelling environment for our game as well as creating the character designs.
    </div>

    <!-- <div id="cursor_container" class="cursor_container art"></div> -->
    <img src="/images/cursor_substitute.gif" id="cursor_substitute" class="cursor_substitute">

    <div class="container" style="justify-content: center; display: flex;">
      <div class="row" style="display: contents;">
        <div class="col-sm-3">
          <div class = "row post">
            <img class="tapeleft" src="images/assets/tape3.png">
            <img class="square art zoom" src="/images/art/portrait.jpg">
            
          </div>
          <div class = "row post">
            <img class="portrait art zoom" src="/images/art/campsite.jpg">
            
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-sm-5">
          <div class = "row post">
            <img class="landscape-3 art zoom" src="/images/art/chibi asha colored.jpg">
            
          </div>
          <div class = "row post">
            <img class="landscape-3 art zoom" src="/images/art/chibi asha.jpg">
            
          </div>
          <div class = "row post">
            <img class="landscape-3 art zoom" src="/images/art/models2.jpg">
            
          </div>
          <div class = "row post">
            <img class="landscape-3 art zoom" src="/images/art/bridge.jpg">
            
          </div>
          <div class = "row post">
            <img class="landscape-3 art zoom" src="/images/art/corvus.jpg">
            
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-sm-3">
          <div class = "row post">
            <img class="taperight" src="images/assets/tape4.png">
            <img class="portrait art zoom" src="/images/art/dark woods.jpg">
            
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="title_container" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 50px">
      <img src="/images/assets/brushstroke1.png" height:100%; top:0;>
      <div class="title">Texture Art</div>
    </div>

    <div class="container" style="font: 16px Catamaran; justify-content: center; display: flex; color: white; font-size: 16px; width: 700px; text-align: center; margin-bottom: 20px;">
      Modelled and textured in Maya, the enviroments that i've created for 'Not A Fairy Tale' were dark and depressing for the first level as to represent the emotional distress that our main character, Asha, experiences.
    </div>

    <div class="container" style="justify-content: center; display: flex; flex-direction: column;">
        <div class="row" style="justify-content: center;">
          <div>
            <img class="texture_art zoom" src="/images/art/a.jpg">
            <span class="caption"></span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <img class="texture_art zoom" src="/images/art/b.jpg">
            <span class="caption"></span>
          </div>
        </div>
